HEADWORD: Smartweed
<hw>Smart"weed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>An acrid plant of the genus <gen>Polygonum</gen> (<spn>Polygonum
Hydropiper</spn>), which produces smarting if applied where the skin is
tender.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

